        NOT READY FOR USE method to extract general shapes from the images and compare them in order to match points. It returns a fit to a rough Euclidean transformation. NOTE that the images may need pre-processing steps before using this. For example, the Brown & Lowe 200? panoramic images of a mountain need to have the sky masked out of the image first.
